'''Dragons E.C.''' is a Spanish team.

== History ==
'''Dragons E.C.''' is a Spanish organization founded in May 2014 and reformed in May 2018, and has teams in ''League of Legends'', ''HearthStone'', and ''Counter Strike Global Offensive''.

